data.description: Stunning 10-years young spacious contemporary Colonial home on a sizable lot with driveway, 2-car garage, and farmer's porch. This 4-bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home will surely impress you, and offers many oversized rooms. Main level offers an open floor plan with hardwood flooring, crown moulding, recessed lighting, fireplaced living room with sliders leading to the exterior deck, open dining room, private office, half bathroom, and expansive custom chef's kitchen with island & breakfast bar. 2nd floor with 4 bedrooms, of which 2 are massive master bedrooms with separate full bathrooms and walk-in-closets. These rooms will leave you in awe. Modernized full bathrooms with tiled flooring, granite tops, and double sinks. Great outdoor entertaining in the private fenced-in backyard with composite deck. Full unfinished basement with steel I-beam offers much possibility, and plenty of storage space. There's nothing to do here, but fight over the bedrooms. Come check out this incredible home!!!
